  "system": {
    "description": "<p>This spell releases waves of energy in all directions from the caster, up to a 20 foot radius sphere, curing 2d8 points of damage to all living creatures in the area of effect, including allies and enemies. The curative version of this spell deals the same damage to undead, while the reverse, <em>harming circle</em>, deals damage to living creatures. In those situations, a successful wisdom save indicates half damage. <em>Harming circle</em> heals undead creatures.</p>",
